refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
arraycollator_get_available_locales
Return the locales available at the time of the call, including registered locales. If a sever error occurs (such as out of memory condition) this will return &false;. If there is no locale data, an empty list will be returned.

  &reftitle.examples;



    collator_get_available_locales example


<?php
$locales = collator_get_available_locales();
printf( "There are %d locales available on this computer.\n", count( $locales ) );
?>


    &example.outputs.similar;


There are 201 locales available on this computer.
